## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-137"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> を呼び出し、元に戻せないドキュメントが存在しない場合、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> はナビゲーションを実行せず、例外がスローされます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-137">If you call <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> and there are not any documents to navigate back to, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> does not perform a navigation and an exception is thrown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-138">必要に応じて、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A> プロパティの値を調べて、戻るドキュメントがあるかどうかを確認できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-138">If you need to, you can inspect the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A> property to determine whether there are documents to navigate back to.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-139">次の例は、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>を呼び出して、前の [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] ドキュメントに戻る方法を示しています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-139">The following example shows how to navigate back to the previous [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document by calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-140">この例では、まず、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>を確認して、戻る [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] ドキュメントがあることを確認します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-140">The example first checks that there are [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] documents to navigate back to by checking <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.CanGoBack%2A>.</span></span>  
  
