## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-156"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> は、それを実装するドキュメントの読み込みが終了する前に呼び出さないでください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-156"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-157"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> イベントを処理することにより、ドキュメントの読み込みが完了したことを検出できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-157">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-158">次の例は、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>を使用して、[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] アプリケーションからドキュメント内のスクリプト関数を呼び出す方法を示しています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-158">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-159">この例では、スクリプト関数にはパラメーターがありません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-159">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-160">[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]から呼び出されるスクリプト関数を実装する [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] ドキュメントを次に示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-160">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-161">[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] ドキュメントでスクリプト関数を呼び出す [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] の実装を次に示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-161">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-169"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> は、それを実装するドキュメントの読み込みが終了する前に呼び出さないでください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-169"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-170"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> イベントを処理することにより、ドキュメントの読み込みが完了したことを検出できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-170">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-171">呼び出しているスクリプトに十分なパラメーター値を渡さないと、値を渡さないパラメーターの値は未定義になります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-171">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-172">パラメーター値が多すぎると、超過した値は無視されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-172">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-173">次の例は、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>を使用して、アプリケーションからドキュメント内のスクリプト関数を呼び出す方法を示しています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-173">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-174">この例では、スクリプト関数にはパラメーターが必要です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-174">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-175">[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]から呼び出されるスクリプト関数を実装するドキュメントを次に示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-175">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-176">[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] ドキュメントでスクリプト関数を呼び出す [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] の実装を次に示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-176">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-190"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> を呼び出すと、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> プロパティの設定と同じ効果があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-190">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-191"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> は、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> の初期化時に移動 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> 最初のドキュメントを宣言によって指定するために、開発者がマークアップから使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-191"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-192"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> メソッドを使用して、エスケープ文字を含む可能性のある URL に移動します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-192">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-193"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> メソッドを使用して、エスケープ文字を含まない <xref:System.Uri> に移動します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-193">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-194">次の例では、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> を使用して、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> メソッドを使用してドキュメントに移動する方法を示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-194">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-212"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> メソッドを使用して、エスケープ文字を含む可能性のある URL に移動します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-212">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-213"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> メソッドを使用して、エスケープ文字を含まない <xref:System.Uri> に移動します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-213">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a5f3-214">次の例では、"about: blank" ターゲットを指定することにより、ドキュメントに移動して新しいブラウザーウィンドウで開く方法を示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a5f3-214">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute. For example, 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
